David and Angie Musselwhite invite you to stop in for lunch or dinner soon!
Open for lunch and dinner Monday through Thursday 11:00am – 8:00pm.
Fridays 11:00am – 9:00pm
Saturdays 11:30am  – 9:00pm
Sundays CLOSED
Musselwhite’s Seafood is easy to find, just at the foot of the Palatka bridge on HWY 17, 386-326-9111.
See you soon!
